<br>
Like i said, the price is determined by what someone will pay -- even if that amount is too much. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elladin>Elladin</A> at: 2/10/03 4:20:59 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=melik001>Melik001</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://goldrush.com/~herd/as-one.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 250<br> <font color=#333333>(2/13/03 6:40:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=381.topic&index=24>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://wreckerofplans.bravepages.com/images/Mage1.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bazaar Morons</span><hr size=1> You would be wurprised what people buy. (and sell for that matter) for inflated prices. <br>
