<br>
there is a bug that happens sometimes where you change a price while already in trader mode but it only changes it for the one item/stack and not all others on your trader.  The trick to ensuring this is fixed (if you are the trader) is to exit and begin trader mode after changing any prices.  This will also serve to 'refresh' your trader in teh /bazaar lists, so that your items show up more frequently when people search for something.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps.<br>
<br>
